{"tid":1212189,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今次已經唔係急救站，係戰地醫院","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T23:20:00.000Z","uid":98642,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5753b26745b9f304e7afbba8a16d069dc1b8b1","tid":1212189,"uid":98642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:37:13.000Z","msg":"一行三十餘人嘅前線急救小隊，去到最後得返十個唔夠，可以選擇嘅只係抌低傷者自己走，或者救得一個得一個。<br />\n<br />\n警察向前推進，我地只可以帶住傷者不停向得退，退到無可後退個陣，我地一餘三十人決定先定將傷者同物資撤走。但同時眼見越來越多人向我哋湧現，我地有20多人決定繼續留守，呼籲大家唔好跑，慢慢撤退同時越來越多中椒，食煙，甚至骨折，人事不醒嘅病人需要我哋幫助。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，我地已經退無可退，得返唯一嘅出口，警察同速龍已經越來越近，但係仲有好多人滯留，尤其是係傷者。我地只可以分頭，做簡單分類，將所適用嘅物資分發同教導佢哋點樣用，之後就只可以等佢哋自己同朋友做簡單自理，從中抽空更多專業嘅同事去處理一啲比較嚴重嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n突然間，一粒臭道彈係我地身後爆炸，劇烈嘅濃煙迅速融入，呢一刻我地仍然有好多病人係急救站，我地只可以叫佢地馬上離開向出口方向奔跑，放棄我地最後嘅急救站，我地一變跑一變攞NS向全身中椒嘅勇士沖洗。我一路回頭數算我地小隊嘅人員數目，同仲有冇傷者跑緊過嚟。到我親眼望到速龍出現，我先和其餘的幾名同事一同向後狂跑。<br />\n<br />\n跑回大隊，眼見大家在路途上，我地先鬆一口氣。但係警察們仍然腳腳推進，似乎唔想俾太多喘息機會我哋。<br />\n<br />\n但對於一啲行動不便嘅傷者，骨折嘅傷者，我地再一次陷入兩難局面。帶走定係唔帶走，如果唔帶走，意味着交俾警察，放棄佢地，佢哋可能會受咁多傷害、控告。如果帶走，我哋點樣帶走。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個骨折傷者，我地只可打個簡單嘅「唔係掛」，做一個簡單固定，再會同佢先行離開。另外一個SOB 人事不醒的傷者，連行路嘅力氣都冇，我地選擇放棄一些物資，抽出人手，將佢抬出去，總算鬆一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n我繼續一路關心同行傷者，一路拎起物資，去到安全地方繼續處理傷者。突然間一道火光從天而降，熾熱嘅氣味重新出現。<br />\n<br />\n全數急救組員和傷者一同吸入大量濃煙，氣管出現了熾熱嘅感覺，呼吸開始加速，我們立即攙扶着傷者再一次踏上走難旅程，向前奔跑。<br />\n<br />\n我立即放下手上物資，背上那名傷者，向唯一的出路奔跑。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉嘅氣味越嚟越濃烈 ，原來佢地將臭彈打係我哋唯一嘅出路中間，Sob病人沒有口罩，迅速吸入大量濃煙，一分鐘後整個人放軟冇力開始暈倒。當中嘅護士立即命令我哋停低，緊急情況需要立即治療。<br />\n但警察仍然保持推進，甚至加速，越來越多嘅叫喊聲係後面傳來。<br />\n<br />\n護士簡單攞咗一套vt，快速決定幫佢落藥，服藥之後病人有些少好轉，但情況仍然非常不穩定，但原有嘅物資已經所剩無幾，警察嘅盾牌已於背後再次出現。<br />\n<br />\n我地只可以再一次，將傷者運送。一邊走一邊留意病人情況，病人寧願沒有好轉，幸好撤退大軍仍然讓出一條緊急通道給我們，一名男途人給予援助，這一次我們的目標是撤去碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n最後無驚冒險，將傷者成功運送去碼頭，我哋立即召喚救護車。我回頭一看，看着熟悉的面孔慢慢出來，所有嘅同事和傷者一同步出，我們才放鬆下來處理傷者。但每一放鬆，警察同速龍就立即跟上，出現在馬頭邊。<br />\n<br />\n十分鐘過後，我地又一次緊張起來，大量傷者同在馬頭。假如速龍發難衝出，我地一定無法再次離開，因為急救員們已經吸入大量催淚煙，同在扶抱傷者時，接觸到傷者衣服上的胡椒，雙臂已經開始紅腫，他們的體力已經大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n我決定先撤走情況危殆的傷者及所有受傷的人員繼續向前撤離，同時警察的防暴隊車隊已經陸續到達了碼頭四周。同行的護士深明危急的形勢，所以我地一齊決定截停一架私家車，懇求他們義載傷員去醫院。<br />\n<br />\n幸好車輛順利出發。<br />\n<br />\n我和剩餘的急救人員會合後，我哋再一次踏上返回碼頭嘅路上。"},{"pid":"2cbd618b95e4619f7c3fed9a4b9419a2709dc040","tid":1212189,"uid":258091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"想喊"},{"pid":"14764e6ea42143b166386bd84a26d06f6c8dbe64","tid":1212189,"uid":53037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664d0d88076f1ce0b57cb6ed7f8af02afd55a9c3","tid":1212189,"uid":242083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd42e133ba8d5fc85966a1e8b7b6abff8481c0d","tid":1212189,"uid":254028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬 今日好彩仲有你地"},{"pid":"93502d09c67ab0f4c3ceb5b22df02590eb23729f","tid":1212189,"uid":128839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd9c5afbe190ed7653f9e4ab67e92ca9f88c034","tid":1212189,"uid":10056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"辛苦你地真係好偉大！"},{"pid":"963d2cf55a306721463f8f2a3bf16f5d697faca7","tid":1212189,"uid":143945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab235fd287f2ce2d2d3a2c88fa0f525ca73c8cc","tid":1212189,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b9b3510d7223fd98f8d5051a5c5cea3a3c7726","tid":1212189,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cf52c28b2b0776d431d728795b3530d3052de7","tid":1212189,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4dc873c449a559625a0b875fd469332da6d68d0","tid":1212189,"uid":211021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"我都係做急救嘅，喺天橋底個位，但除咗個口罩同手套外就咩都冇，第一次射催淚彈嗰時已經頂唔順去咗外面，原本諗住返再入去幫喺最前面嘅嗰班人，不過嗰時就已經射第二次催淚彈，最後第三次射嗰時個人真係頂唔順，交低盒哮喘藥你其他急救嘅人就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f03e5afe03bd91436382a5e92d929b8546b61e","tid":1212189,"uid":75148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523702c89e686873251c6cc3e67c3c8e000b4191","tid":1212189,"uid":63651,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"真係想喊，究竟邊個先係恃強凌弱既暴徒呢"},{"pid":"a430663c3fe4dbf9dcc59eef7f0b7d97a7d229e2","tid":1212189,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc92cbf2742888e6a813f273eeae4808383d5205","tid":1212189,"uid":136457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:54:34.000Z","msg":"英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11064765f7f931214a9ea7943f71eb46eb436dc8","tid":1212189,"uid":69314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:57:05.000Z","msg":"大家有共識行動，請幫手推下，share出去<br />\n<br />\n613行動部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c20dee115d9253362b46d0754b3a8c6b45c5f22c","tid":1212189,"uid":9412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"你地係英雄 全場唔理危險不斷周圍走只為咗救傷者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次有人大叫急救你地就即刻出現走過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031a6521c10357eb39ddb1be6e8e558a10453d8b","tid":1212189,"uid":152612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:03:38.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂"},{"pid":"5fd01014640d7561b522b8016be0a1f317b51c59","tid":1212189,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38479d9c1694f75dfe829e454a57e3cba5061ecf","tid":1212189,"uid":98642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:20:00.000Z","msg":"我地唔係英雄，只係希望大家知道我地會係後面支援住前面受傷嘅每一個。<br />\n<br />\n完全唔忍心見到大家俾人打到頭破血流，仲要拉去差館。你地入得黎急救站，我地就盡最後嘅能力保護受左傷嘅你地。<br />\n<br />\n呢一點只係我哋唯一可以幫到前線你地嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}